{
  "stem": "1641.5",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So just a bit of more patience and we'll lick the Americans completely and we'll wipe out England and we'll win for sure.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That's what he said, even on the day when the Russians entered Berlin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Victory is ours, no doubt about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So that we could read the paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We could read the SS man's paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That was a big benefit of-- of the Jewish doctor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the other big benefit was that we had one doctor for 1,200 people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And every morning, he was holding one hour or two hour surgery hours-- you know, and he had to go to other blocks, too.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Well, anybody with a big rotten-- big-- you know, you got these swollen, rotten things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So one day, I went up to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He just took out his pocket knife.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he said, look, I can't do everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But I'll do this one, that one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I'll do these four.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he just cut-- cut into it with his pocket night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He pushed out the thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Then he gets some toilet papers, which he stuck on in the cut here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He had about four or five cuts he made.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was good, because he pushed out all the infected parts.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Say, I can't do much with your gums, unfortunately, which was indeed very unfortunate, because the daily bread portion-- see, what happened in April, by that time, all order-- law and order broke down you know, in that part of Austria.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "There was no more supplies from-- from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Hungary was already in Russian hands.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "No more food coming to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I have to--",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
